Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:49.17,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}在謎團重重的此世之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:51.17,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}將橫行的棋子落下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:53.71,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}If I could burn it all down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:56.84,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}尋覓不見出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:59.51,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HEFF1EA&\bord0}深切祈求的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:02.05,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}到底消失去了哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:03.89,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&HFFFFFF&}Pray all night long
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:06.10,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&HFFFFFF&}你是否能聽見
