Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:11.77,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}在棋盤格上微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:17.40,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}繪出的是最激烈的終局
