Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:25.83,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}勝負在此一舉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:28.00,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}靠才能召喚勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:30.71,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HEFF1EA&\bord0}Save my life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:33.34,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H6E7381&\bord0}這是單程的軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:36.09,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H36373A&\blur4}不知後悔為何物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:38.34,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H36373A&\blur4}三番五次地嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:41.13,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}完美地checkmate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:57.40,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你  叫格蕾絲來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:58.39,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:05.59,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,正好藉此機會  把我名下的寶石都整理一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.49,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:11.16,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,說實話我呢  有一位未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:14.79,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是那位非常美麗的未婚妻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:18.00,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,就是那位非常美麗的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:21.89,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,但她缺乏見識  還沒有判斷能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:24.29,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,什麼東西都撿回來收集
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:27.60,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,明明我都提醒過她好多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:33.46,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,他這話是想說  是我的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:38.23,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,公爵大人  其實我也有一位未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:42.56,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你說的是那位長相出眾的未婚夫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:45.81,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,就是那位長相還算出眾的未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:50.31,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,對未婚妻不僅不尊重  還一點都不體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:52.64,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,有的沒的都亂說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:56.21,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,明明我都已經千叮嚀萬囑咐過他了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:00.95,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:06.93,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,而且他手上動作還不乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:12.64,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,努爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.19,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,看見這些寶石了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:23.24,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我正是要對我非常美麗的未婚妻表示尊重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:24.93,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,才把她帶來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:29.25,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,這樣你總算能感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:33.06,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那位長相還算出眾的未婚夫的些許體貼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:38.21,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,溫奈特公爵閣下  讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:39.41,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,格蕾絲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:44.50,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  這就是您傳說中的未婚妻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:49.44,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我還以為  閣下您對女性不感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:52.90,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,看來只是至今為止沒找到您中意的對象而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:55.03,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那可真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.11,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,不愧是格蕾絲夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:58.50,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,被看破了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:02.12,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我正好進了一些好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:03.84,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你要不要一起看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.49,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,樂意至極
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:09.81,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,它叫人魚之淚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:13.86,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,曾在德瓦莎拍賣中拍出了最高價
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.34,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你覺得呢  還合你心意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:18.92,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我覺得很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.53,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:24.10,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,當然  不管哪件都很美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:28.23,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那麼  店裡全部的東西我都要了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:29.24,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:31.20,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,不愧是公爵閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.46,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那就請先收下這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:38.79,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,除了這個  其他的都送到府邸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:41.52,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:49.06,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我真的可以收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.94,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,跟你很配哦  萊利娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.76,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,不  不能太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:45.27,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你累嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.96,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我們也沒怎麼走路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:52.23,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我聽說你給女僕放假了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:53.56,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:58.08,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,要是連感恩節都不能回家  也太可憐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:00.88,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,雖說如此  其實這只是藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:03.92,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我想悠閒地獨處  哪怕只有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.71,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:20.55,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,萊利娜  我有點事要處理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:22.76,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,現在要外出一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:25.20,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好的  路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:36.40,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:37.72,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:39.88,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:41.43,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,海莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.83,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼還沒走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:47.75,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,這次真的非常感謝您能給我們放假
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.33,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好好享受感恩節吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:52.85,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:56.69,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,其實  我是有點事要告訴您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.53,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:03.41,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,請絕對不要在西館最裡面的房間照鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:05.43,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,鏡子？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:09.70,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好像有個女僕被輪到去那值班巡邏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:12.76,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,然後在那裡有人和她搭話了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:14.24,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:19.30,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,有靈魂被封印在房間裡的鏡子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:22.31,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,當與鏡中靈魂的眼神對視時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:24.39,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好像就會有人和你說話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.36,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,會…會說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:32.82,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,它會說  我什麼事都會告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:35.16,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,什麼事都？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:41.09,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,已經這個點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:42.60,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那我就告退了  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:45.97,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我得去收拾回家的行李了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:57.67,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,要是真的有那樣一面鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:59.78,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我只有一件事想問它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:03.32,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,故事真正的女主角  貝阿特麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:06.20,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,她現在身在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:25.00,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:28.13,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,早知道我乖乖待在房間裡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:32.80,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,就是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:36.04,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,果然好嚇人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:44.08,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,什麼啊  原來是鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:09:59.32,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:01.84,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我真的得跟它對視才行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:05.03,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,什麼事情都會告訴我根本就不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.59,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,萬一被詛咒了怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:15.27,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,有聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:20.04,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我雖然聽不太清  可剛才確實…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:34.66,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:39.28,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,怎麼嚇成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:43.38,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那是因為  我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:45.60,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,看到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:47.92,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,看到了鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:50.47,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:56.07,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你不會覺得我在說謊吧  我說的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:59.99,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那我明天把神官叫過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.93,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,話說  你為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:06.13,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我有東西忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:09.11,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你是不是因為擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.80,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,不  我只是有東西忘拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.44,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那你等會就回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:25.57,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,不  到明天再處理也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:27.72,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我送你回房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:30.05,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:41.35,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,可是  他為什麼回來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.99,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,雖然他說忘帶東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:46.31,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,但會在這個時間回來拿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:50.28,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,難道真的是因為擔心我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:52.07,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:53.76,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:55.44,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.90,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,麻煩你特地跑一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:09.38,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那麼晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.40,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你不害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:14.18,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,害怕什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:16.77,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,鬼魂  你看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:19.92,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,嘛  雖說是看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:23.14,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,不會哭喪著臉睡不著覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.93,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,夠了  你快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:26.61,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,別那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:29.20,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:34.10,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你睡著之前我都在這陪著你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.19,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:44.74,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那努爾去睡床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.39,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我睡椅子就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:53.16,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,幹嘛…努爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:56.47,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.55,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,又不是第一次了  事到如今你在緊張什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:21.97,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你這種說法要是被其他人聽見了會誤會的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:25.91,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我可不想當讓自己未婚妻睡在椅子上的人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:28.28,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,所以麻煩睡在我身旁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.10,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,這本書  我可以看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:40.87,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,講述騎士和公主之間愛而無果的戀愛小說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:44.40,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,可我覺得不太合你的胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:47.17,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,沒關係  我不在意題材
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:03.99,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,不行  完全睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:07.64,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,努爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:08.68,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.11,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你讀到哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:14.05,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,兩個主角在舞會上相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:18.45,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那裡啊  有沒有覺得令人心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:19.76,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:23.60,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,太滑稽了  反而充滿了戲劇性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.00,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,滑稽？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:27.59,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,兩個人偶遇以後就一見鍾情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:30.36,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,因為一場偶然的事故又不得不分離
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:33.84,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,幾個月後  又再次碰巧在舞會上相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.96,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,一系列都是巧合所以滑稽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:38.48,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,未免也太不現實了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:42.68,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,明明自己也是戀愛小說的主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:44.00,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.33,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,一味追求現實性的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:49.51,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你永遠體會不到心動和浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.43,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你讀到騎士告白的地方了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:54.15,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.21,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你快看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:57.51,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,超級心動的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:58.29,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,萊利娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:14:59.76,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你不睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:01.83,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.50,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:08.21,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,啊…是是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:10.80,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,已經很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:11.81,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:13.89,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:53.12,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我變得有點怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.21,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,奧布萊恩伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.90,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,啊  溫奈特公爵閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:22.71,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.95,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,聽說你為執行任務而遠征中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.64,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是的  已經圓滿完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:34.07,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,原來如此  陛下在裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:36.00,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,等等  閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:38.15,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,可以請您稍微等一會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:05.76,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,西亞特里斯陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:07.60,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我是娜奧美·奧布萊恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:12.34,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,陛下！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.33,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,您該起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:24.18,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,娜奧美  你為何如此神經大條
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:26.98,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你至少應該要敲門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:28.04,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我敲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:31.11,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我沒聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:36.36,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,至今為止您一次也沒聽到我的敲門聲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:37.81,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:41.12,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,或許您應該去檢查一下您的聽力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:45.89,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,啊…說起來感覺好像聽到了敲門聲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.94,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,啊不  確實聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.84,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那就最好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:53.78,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,哦…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:57.11,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我從剛剛那位女士那裡聽到了有趣的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:57.84,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.99,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,聽說我在生死之間徘徊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:05.80,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我那可愛的弟弟努爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:09.03,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,有了一位深愛著的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:12.60,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好像是叫…萊莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:15.48,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,生死之間徘徊也太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:17.43,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,而且不是叫萊莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.75,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是麥米倫家族的萊利娜大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:25.46,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,查爾莫斯王國的現任國王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:29.60,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,在床上還能聽到這樣的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:33.62,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,這足以說明我有多愛我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:34.96,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:39.14,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,陛下  你看起來已經痊癒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:41.51,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,奇斯  好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:43.06,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,努爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:44.07,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我在這
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:47.80,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,哦~努爾  你在那啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:50.26,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好像有個人不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:51.68,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那個紅色眼睛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:56.10,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,亞丹的話有別的事情還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:59.06,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,嗯…還真是稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.93,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,既然大家都到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:07.80,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我們為了明天舉杯慶祝一下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.24,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,會期終於結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:19.09,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,被否決的法案在幾年內不能再被提出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:23.91,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,所以我們暫時阻止了「暴發戶防止法」的成立
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:28.85,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,也就是說沒必要再把玉璽藏起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:31.94,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,關於陛下的落馬事故
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:35.35,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,從馬的體內檢測到了興奮劑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:39.40,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,果然…從那匹馬奇怪的樣子來看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.78,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,就知道不可能是巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:43.32,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:46.05,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,這是由貝內特伯爵精心策劃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:48.63,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,暗殺國王計劃的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:50.53,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,貝內特啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:54.47,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我要是死了那傢伙肯定是最開心的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:20:00.00,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,貝內特伯爵的話會將陛下的屍體掛在廣場上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:01.14,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,再在旁邊跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:03.16,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,肯定還會唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:08.04,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你總是能把這麼嚇人的事情說得這麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.24,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,您誤會了  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.05,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,話說回來  努爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:16.02,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,聽說你多了個未婚妻？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:18.84,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,名字好像是叫…拉莉安娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.56,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,剛剛已經告訴過您了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:24.98,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是萊利娜·麥米倫大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:27.67,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,對對  萊利娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:30.58,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,在我因服用鎮靜劑而昏迷的這段時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:33.27,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你的心境發生了什麼變化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:37.97,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,這個嘛…有很多原因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.66,0:20:39.35,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:47.40,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:53.25,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我給您放在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:55.67,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你  海莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:59.04,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,秋雨時期已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:02.31,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,很快要真正開始變冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:04.16,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,秋雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:07.12,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好像想起了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.19,0:21:08.10,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:21.40,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,「會期終於結束，玉璽的行蹤何去何從？」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:23.84,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.27,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:30.68,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我為什麼會忘掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:40.79,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,會期結束的前一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:42.77,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,在溫奈特家族的墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:47.65,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,按照原著的話  她會出現在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:50.92,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,金髮的  貝阿特麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:11.06,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,也就是說  你的婚約可以作廢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:07.59,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(600,800)\blur5}変わりのない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:13.64,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(600,800)\blur5}夢の続きを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:20.40,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(600,800)\blur5}誰かの私でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.69,0:22:25.86,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(600,800)\blur5}それでも今日も息をしている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.65,0:22:32.20,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}星降る夜に流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:39.12,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}あなたは何処へ向かうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:46.72,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}物語にはない　終わらない運命が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:52.01,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}叶うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:23:00.73,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}Always and Forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:08.32,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}ただ　生きるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:16.83,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}揺れた灯りが儚く消える前に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:22.79,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}遠く　遠く　離れていても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:31.68,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}強く　強く　愛せますように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:07.59,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(600,800)\blur5}未曾改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:13.64,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(600,800)\blur5}夢境的延續
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:20.40,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(600,800)\blur5}無論是誰  亦或是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.69,0:22:25.86,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(600,800)\blur5}即便如此今天也依然活著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.65,0:22:32.20,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}在那個星河流淌的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:39.12,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}你將前往何方？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:46.72,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}故事中不存在的  未完的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:52.01,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}若能夠實現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:23:00.73,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}Always and Forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:08.32,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}只是  活著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:16.83,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}在搖曳的燈光飄渺著熄滅之前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:22.79,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}即使離得很遠  很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:31.68,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}也希望能夠堅強地愛下去
